  "description": "<h3>Back of Case - Nintendo DS (US) (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/power-play-pool/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3>POweR PLAY POOL brings the classic game of pool to the Nintendo DS in full 3D. Represent your nation and become the world's greatest pool player. Play leagues and tournaments wirelessly against a friend or against the computer. Play against 15 other pool sharks across four varieties of pool: UK 8 Ball Pool, US 8 Ball Pool, US 9 Ball Pool and the super tense Killer Pool!\n<ul>\n<li>A fully 3D pool table with top-down view on the second screen.</li>\n<li>Play multiplayer over Wireless LAN in tournaments and leagues.</li>\n<li>Four Unique Styles - UK 8 Ball Pool, US 8 Ball Pool, US 9 Ball Pool and Killer Pool.</li>\n<li>Pool Play Your Way: Choose between button or stylus control.</li>\n</ul>",
